sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant RASA as Rasa NLU Runtime
    participant MSG as Message
    participant PRE as VietnameseTextPreprocessor
    participant SEG as VnCoreNLP Segmenter
    participant PHO as PhoBERTIntentClassifier
    participant TOK as PhoBERT Tokenizer
    participant MODEL as PhoBERT Model
    participant RANK as Confidence / Ranking
    participant REG as RegexEntityExtractor
    participant SYN as EntitySynonymMapper
    participant FB as FallbackClassifier

    RASA->>PHO: process(messages)
    loop Moi user message
        PHO->>MSG: get(TEXT)
        PHO->>PRE: preprocess(text)
        PRE-->>PHO: text da chuan hoa
        PHO->>PHO: Bo ky tu . va ;
        PHO->>SEG: word_segment(text)
        SEG-->>PHO: text da tach tu tieng Viet
        PHO->>TOK: encode_plus(max_seq_length)
        TOK-->>PHO: input_ids, attention_mask
        PHO->>MODEL: forward inference
        MODEL-->>PHO: logits va embedding
        PHO->>RANK: softmax, margin, OOD factor, top-k
        RANK-->>PHO: intent_id, confidence, intent_ranking
        PHO->>MSG: set intent
        PHO->>MSG: set intent_ranking
    end
    RASA->>REG: Extract regex entities
    REG-->>RASA: entities
    RASA->>SYN: Map entity synonyms
    SYN-->>RASA: normalized entities
    RASA->>FB: Kiem tra confidence va ambiguity
    alt Dat nguong
        FB-->>RASA: Giu intent PhoBERT
    else Khong dat nguong
        FB-->>RASA: Chuyen sang nlu_fallback
    end
    RASA-->>RASA: parse_data = intent + confidence + ranking + entities
